name: Kidnapping Evidence
description: Veine Coructie has collected the evidence you collected from the Pator 6, as well as some of the data found from the bug you planted. With this in hand, they're ready to smoke the kid out by causing a big media stir. There's no hiding when an entire population is out to get you. Sure, you should probably take this to the FIO, but who knows how effective this will be?
